= CBRAIN Project : BrainPortal

Welcome the the CBRAIN BrainPortal application!

== About BrainPortal

BrainPortal is the frontend side of the CBRAIN architecture. It is a
Rails application that provides a web-based graphical user interface.

== The main Ruby classes that are of interest are:

Userfile:: this models the user's files are entries in the database; they are ActiveRecord objects
DataProvider:: this models an external provider for the contents of the userfiles; they are also ActiveRecord objects
DrmaaTask:: this models a task request to a cluster, and its evolving states. They are ActiveResource objects.

